# Onboarding Route Guidance

- Keep onboarding as a short, linear wizard with clear progress at each step.
- Preserve the 4-step setup intent: profile, branding, legal/tax, first project.
- Make SOW upload the emotional peak of onboarding and transition cleanly into AI extraction.
- Do not auto-publish AI output from onboarding; require explicit user confirmation.
- Use resilient optimistic UI only where rollback is safe; otherwise show deterministic server state.
